   "source": [
    "# LDDMM: how to visualize registration results?"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "First, run [LDDMM: how to register a mesh to a template?](./lddmm_register_mesh_template.ipynb)."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 1,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stderr",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "No CUDA runtime is found, using CUDA_HOME='/usr'\n"
     ]
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "from pathlib import Path\n",
    "\n",
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "import pyvista as pv\n",
    "\n",
    "import polpo.lddmm as plddmm\n",
    "import polpo.utils as putils\n",
    "from polpo.plot.pyvista import RegisteredMeshesGifPlotter\n",
    "from polpo.preprocessing import Map, Sorter\n",
    "from polpo.preprocessing.mesh.io import PvReader\n",
    "from polpo.preprocessing.path import FileFinder, IsFileType, PathShortener"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 2,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "STATIC_VIZ = True\n",
    "\n",
    "if STATIC_VIZ:\n",
    "    pv.set_jupyter_backend(\"static\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 3,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "STRUCT_NAME = \"PostHipp\"\n",
    "\n",
    "OUTPUTS_DIR = Path(\"results\") / f\"registration_{STRUCT_NAME.lower()}\"\n",
    "REGISTRATION_DIR = OUTPUTS_DIR / \"registration\""
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 4,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "_custom_order = putils.custom_order([\"source\", \"target\"])\n",
    "name2shortname = PathShortener(init_index=-1) + (\n",
    "    lambda x: x.split(\".\")[0].split(\"_\")[1]\n",
    ")\n",
    "\n",
    "filenames = (\n",
    "    FileFinder(\n",
    "        OUTPUTS_DIR,\n",
    "        rules=IsFileType(\"vtk\"),\n",
    "    )\n",
    "    + Sorter(lambda x: _custom_order(name2shortname(x)))\n",
    ")()\n",
    "\n",
    "pv_reader = Map(PvReader())\n",
    "\n",
    "source, target = pv_reader(filenames)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Template and control points"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 5,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "cp, momenta = plddmm.io.load_cp_and_momenta(REGISTRATION_DIR)\n",
    "\n",
    "template = plddmm.io.load_template(REGISTRATION_DIR, as_pv=True)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "Confirm that source and template are the same mesh."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 6,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/plain": [
       "0.0"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 6,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "np.amax(np.abs(template.points - source.points))"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "Visualize template with control points."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 7,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/jpeg": "",
      "image/png": "",
      "text/plain": [
       "<PIL.Image.Image image mode=RGB size=1024x768>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "pl = pv.Plotter()\n",
    "\n",
    "pl.add_mesh(template, show_edges=True)\n",
    "\n",
    "# TODO: add velocity and allow for filtering\n",
    "# control_points.set_active_scalars(\"Velocity\")\n",
    "pl.add_points(pv.PolyData(cp))\n",
    "\n",
    "pl.show()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Target and reconstructed meshes"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 8,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "reconstructed = plddmm.io.load_deterministic_atlas_reconstruction(\n",
    "    REGISTRATION_DIR, as_pv=True\n",
    ")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 9,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/jpeg": "",

     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "pl = pv.Plotter()\n",
    "\n",
    "pl.add_mesh(reconstructed, show_edges=True)\n",
    "pl.add_mesh(target, opacity=0.55)\n",
    "\n",
    "pl.show()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",

    "## Flow"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 10,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "flow_meshes = plddmm.io.load_deterministic_atlas_flow(\n",
    "    REGISTRATION_DIR,\n",
    "    as_pv=True,\n",
    ")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 11,

   "source": [
    "gif_dir = OUTPUTS_DIR / \"_images\"\n",
    "gif_dir.mkdir(exist_ok=True)\n",
    "\n",
    "gif_name = gif_dir / \"flow.gif\"\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "pl = RegisteredMeshesGifPlotter(\n",
    "    gif_name=gif_name.as_posix(),\n",
    ")\n",
    "\n",
    "pl.add_meshes(flow_meshes)\n",
    "pl.close()\n",
    "\n",
    "pl.show()"
